cleanname: Percent of Population with Vehicle Access
description: The percentage of the population with access to a vehicle.

cleanname: County Percentage of Voting Age Citizens
description: The number of citizens in this tract who are voting age divided by the county's total number of voting age citizens.

The percent of employed county residents in a tract out of the total employed county residents in the county.
The percentage of the population that is Hispanic or Latino.
The percentage of the population that has limited English proficiency.
The number of voters who voted at a polling place divided by the total number of voters who voted at a polling place in the county.
The total population density per square kilometer.

cleanname: Percent of the Population in Poverty
description: The percentage of the population with income below the poverty level.
